了老板原来年糕入锅时马上把蛋液淋上去，难怪了这么Q这么香，超赞 以上是我这次霸王餐品尝中喜欢的几道特色菜，当然还有其他象新鲜的血蛤，特色炒海瓜子，还有潮州代表的虾蟹粥，对了，功夫汤忘记说了，那汤料叫一个大气，里面有鸽子、排骨、海马、羊肚菌，88一壶可以倒六七杯，大补阿，餐后还有甜品海石花葛仙米，这个我也是第一次吃，海石花象木瓜里的籽，这碗冰冰凉凉的很合女生口味哦。  \",\"quality\":null,\"uniqkey\":\"24af0566a30ccf8c020165b993a64421\",\"src\":\"new_dianping\",\"former_source\":\"new_dianping\",\"cn_name\":\"大众点评\",\"from\":\"dianping.com\",\"comment_url\":\"http://www.dianping.com/shop/6061476/review_all\",\"comment_url_mobile\":\"http://www.dianping.com/shop/6061476/review_all\",\"uid\":\"16461975845522629598:new_dianping\",\"mark_source\":20,\"mark_duration\":10,\"mark_multimedia\":60,\"mark_content\":35,\"mark_userscore\":10,\"mark_total\":135,\"comment_num\":48,\"cmt_id\":\"24af0566a30ccf8c020165b993a64421\",\"isAgree\":null,\"favorNum\":0,\"reply\":null},{\"overall_rating\":5,\"one_url\":\"http://www.dianping.com/shop/6061476/review_all\",\"taste_rating\":null,\"user_name\":\"路西没有法\",\"environment_rating\":null,\"cmt_icons\":{\"comment_icon\":[]},\"one_url_mobile\":\"http://www.dianping.com/shop/6061476/review_all\",\"service_rating\":null,\"pics\":[{\"pic_url\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/e_jHnlNtGg1It_g6gbWV4dSUcNgPRgfPIBozqw6IRKXUiURwWfT9vPdxmK5NZTF8joJrvItByyS4HHaWdXyO_DrXIaWutJls2xCVbatkhjUNNiIYVnHvzugZCuBITtvjski7YaLlHpkrQUr5euoQrg.jpg\",\"big_photo\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/e_jHnlNtGg1It_g6gbWV4dSUcNgPRgfPIBozqw6IRKXUiURwWfT9vPdxmK5NZTF8joJrvItByyS4HHaWdXyO_DrXIaWutJls2xCVbatkhjUNNiIYVnHvzugZCuBITtvjski7YaLlHpkrQUr5euoQrg.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":2},{\"pic_url\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/MwOKfWnskAE9hTLgGEJo87zvZJvOQARsvgpG1tbtH0202gP6n_pP8IiNC4YjV8AhjoJrvItByyS4HHaWdXyO_DrXIaWutJls2xCVbatkhjUNNiIYVnHvzugZCuBITtvjski7YaLlHpkrQUr5euoQrg.jpg\",\"big_photo\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/MwOKfWnskAE9hTLgGEJo87zvZJvOQARsvgpG1tbtH0202gP6n_pP8IiNC4YjV8AhjoJrvItByyS4HHaWdXyO_DrXIaWutJls2xCVbatkhjUNNiIYVnHvzugZCuBITtvjski7YaLlHpkrQUr5euoQrg.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":2},{\"pic_url\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/GpckrYD7ysSpcflhxfa8S3UGKPDQlf_qnrYw6