INSERT INTO `place_comment` VALUES (347, '0a15c7ecdd1296e5ec74f883', '感谢点评粑粑福利，抽中霸王餐😜😜火辣辣以前去过新塘路店，在天虹对面，很醒目，这次来的是衣之家总店。位置很好找，但是导错路了，竟然停在隔壁酒店的地下停车场，顺便吐槽一下停车场，像一个没竣工的烂尾楼！！！火辣辣吃的是衢州菜，以前就知道衢州人很能吃辣，但是没想到可以辣哭两个好盆友～【麻辣鸭头】不能吃辣的孩纸，还是不要玩火***了，呡一小口都会觉得辣到没娘，尤其是饿肚子时候，不要轻易尝试，很容易引起xx恐慌。不过味道还好。【汪刺鱼】汪刺鱼本身肉质就很鲜嫩，也很入味，一份大概有8条左右，两个人吃足够了。【豇豆】豇豆晒成干，与辣椒一起翻炒，微辣，劲道有嚼劲，吃完还想吃。【家常豆腐】家常的烧法，放上各种辣椒，咸鲜有辣味，豆腐也很嫩。经理特别好，找到以后很热情的询问，而且还赠送了一扎水果汁，整体还可以，就是鸭头实在太辣了，小朋友吃的时候要注意。', '[{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/b0993ae6a7707423c287aa7685695e13\",\"pic_pv\":49},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/7bc200228121fe112ccb84d7885503f8\",\"pic_pv\":64},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/7ab1df51abfe6ce6b12e86b08284a93e\",\"pic_pv\":65},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/22b2b30b3e37efafb6ad97e8ec1bb687\",\"pic_pv\":40},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/d08060f4db2e9473581fa3053d084cc5\",\"pic_pv\":36},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/61d39418c5b74bc1f2c0f1e6374791f6\",\"pic_pv\":33},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/03e570c1581ed07a3592c49573b354d8\",\"pic_pv\":30},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/3086e325ba553230e82ac2214d6dd206\",\"pic_pv\":9},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/e356398b06c3b5189218eb6104932cb2\",\"pic_pv\":7}]', 0, '2018-04-23 00:00', NULL, '婧子IRIS', 'http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/9c6a462eada0f273833e5a6ac8a15641?type=pic', 4.00, 1);
INSERT INTO `place_comment` VALUES (348, '0a15c7ecdd1296e5ec74f883', '据说这家店以辣出名，我自认为还算能吃辣，所以就来试试了！店很好找，招牌很明显，但从外面看，感觉有点简陋，不过其实进店后还不错的，很大！重要的事情三说遍！！！不能吃辣的朋友千万别去😂不能吃辣的朋友千万别去😂不能吃辣的朋友千万别去😂整体吃下来听到旁边桌客人说得最多的就是辣！还有一桌吃了几口后剩下的都打包了，因为实在吃不下去！👉鸭头刚开始先稍微嗦了一口，就感觉到浓浓的辣味，在接下来吃的过程中，简直辣到嘴不是自己的了！除了辣感觉不到任何别的味道了！并不是红油那种香辣，而就是纯纯的辣，一口鸭头两三口西瓜汁才勉强吃下去！👉汪刺鱼鱼特别的嫩，吃起来没有鸭头那么辣，很香，滑嫩的口感，非常推荐这道菜！👉包心菜，烧豆腐就是普通的家常菜，没什么特别的地方，但是特别油......感觉像是油泡出来的！总之，偏清淡口的朋友千万别去，重口的朋友去试试吧！', '[{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/9e18bf00a63b10d19319a24a19aab0d5\",\"pic_pv\":18},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/d83c9ea0c2ee8acd84d93050e25e70ec\",\"pic_pv\":20},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/488664121b2d535c01b0caa884449716\",\"pic_pv\":17},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/de6ccd402638cdb822d77e17492896ae\",\"pic_pv\":9},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/24dff05ec9abf9a7ca2a35f159242e9f\",\"pic_pv\":9},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/e0014850dd62a6883425349d5f99f716\",\"pic_pv\":10},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/7975b8f2df697370df35782247a55873\",\"pic_pv\":12},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/d37d0377b5dc14100d894c2debc4cc9f\",\"pic_pv\":12},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/2a8a6625ad5e088a4dea90c61b854287\",\"pic_pv\":3},{\"pic_url\":\"http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/f7acf0369137b541436e1643b3a39cd8\",\"pic_pv\":1}]', 0, '2018-04-22 00:00', NULL, '險』', 'http://store.is.autonavi.com/showpic/9c6a462eada0f273833e5a6ac8a15641?type=pic', 4.00, 1);
INSERT INTO `place_comment` VALUES (349, '0a15c7ecdd1296e5ec74f883', '衢州人特别爱吃辣，衢州三头一掌就是以辣著称，是衢州地方特色风味美食。地址:天成路，城东衣之家一楼，紧邻皇冠大酒店。环境及服务:如果不看店名，还以为进了一家创意餐馆，环境还是有特色的，就是服务差了点，让阿姨倒杯水，直接回复热水太烫你喝不了（太委婉了😢）。菜品:【手抓小龙虾】小龙虾是在夏季的时候销售最多，店内有的话必须点一份。用炒辣的锅来烧龙虾，必然也是辣么，不过还是很过瘾的。【椒盐鸭头】失传多年了，今天又重新刺激了味蕾，鸭头上桌皮脆内嫩，色泽红亮，分分秒清盘是肯定的，推荐。【鱼头】此菜香气扑鼻，美味可口，又香又辣，既醒神又开胃，同时搭配鸡爪，真是鼻涕眼泪一把一把。', '[{\"pic_url\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/114XGG6CcnPAFKtoIegQe1vJ0fAZX9EQMt-c4sKGAKOlQYCdP4TH53ryBRZS7fKNTYGVDmosZWTLal1WbWRW3A.jpg\",\"big_photo\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/114XGG6CcnPAFKtoIegQe1vJ0fAZX9EQMt-c4sKGAKOlQYCdP4TH53ryBRZS7fKNTYGVDmosZWTLal1WbWRW3A.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":12},{\"pic_url\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/blsVqVclj1V7Gx0Hn6_-Xu0NtY55_AT6OPlvYOeh_RIq7pxVk7nzsiM7RumjiRGjTYGVDmosZWTLal1WbWRW3A.jpg\",\"big_photo\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/blsVqVclj1V7Gx0Hn6_-Xu0NtY55_AT6OPlvYOeh_RIq7pxVk7nzsiM7RumjiRGjTYGVDmosZWTLal1WbWRW3A.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":10},{\"pic_url\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/7tbmQ6Q-VZLcb6lYzyFD8OTUUNcEHeur9fMuNswAEYlg6j9t0CW1LrTJzdCeGhEmTYGVDmosZWTLal1WbWRW3A.jpg\",\"big_photo\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/7tbmQ6Q-VZLcb6lYzyFD8OTUUNcEHeur9fMuNswAEYlg6j9t0CW1LrTJzdCeGhEmTYGVDmosZWTLal1WbWRW3A.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":11},{\"pic_url\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/mqpuReLAih6taiVg0OSaAODe-6YqkYKnHbibF6b2Ltgb3fULDvxJT1BFUqCYISgVTYGVDmosZWTLal1WbWRW3A.jpg\",\"big_photo\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/mqpuReLAih6taiVg0OSaAODe-6YqkYKnHbibF6b2Ltgb3fULDvxJT1BFUqCYISgVTYGVDmosZWTLal1WbWRW3A.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":3},{\"pic_url\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/FPRfvMXpEMKvIZjXodFEUxYZFdkY8Tesz-x6BVleb0c9Vv-K7K1lRSAtc0Rwz-rWTYGVDmosZWTLal1WbWRW3A.jpg\",\"big_photo\":\"http://qcloud.dpfile.com/pc/FPRfvMXpEMKvIZjXodFEUxYZFdkY8Tesz-x6BVleb0c9Vv-K7K1lRSAtc0Rwz-rWTYGVDmosZWTLal1WbWRW3A.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":1}]', 0, '2017-06-29 00:00', NULL, '小笙品濕', 'https://p0.meituan.net/userheadpicbackend/b798cbba4030cb22c2d9af92a8ca8a3015485.jpg%4048w_48h_1e_1c_1l%7Cwatermark%3D0', 3.00, 1);
INSERT INTO `place_comment` VALUES (350, 'fd007c5e519a6a75a8f7296b', '名人名家在杭州有多家分店，经营得蛮成功的，菜式很丰富；特别推荐位于秋涛北路76号中豪大酒店三楼的分店，这家店经营多年，去年新装修完，今年1月1号以全新面貌正式迎客，无论店堂环境还是菜式品种，都有了很大的提升，那些饭前冷盘小吃花样多、口味佳，其中的鸭舌、酱萝卜、天目山笋、海带丝个人觉得特别好吃；以海鲜为主题的主菜更是让人回味无穷，特别推荐：椒盐小青龙、泡菜龙胆鱼、清蒸子蟹、奉化芋头炖咸肉。俗话说得好～不试不知道，我就觉得吃过忘不了。', '[{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/\",\"pic_pv\":407},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/\",\"pic_pv\":407},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100e0e00000075iha3DBB.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":6},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/\",\"pic_pv\":407},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/\",\"pic_pv\":407},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100p0e00000075ige5A7D.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":2},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/\",\"pic_pv\":407},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100t0e00000075it8E5B0.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":2},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/10070e00000075ivk1EEB.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":2},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/\",\"pic_pv\":407},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100r0e00000075hoq8438.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":0},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/\",\"pic_pv\":407}]', 0, '2017-03-18 20:37', NULL, '大DDDDDD', 'https://images4.c-ctrip.com/target/t1/headphoto/136/299/437/649eb217e3e54746b7a53b8665e14b00_C_180_180.jpg', 4.00, 1);
INSERT INTO `place_comment` VALUES (351, 'fd007c5e519a6a75a8f7296b', '沈一点717落胃节活动的福利，名人名家澳门广场店的双人套餐。&#x0A;朋友来杭州玩，住在东站附近，正好接了他们过来吃饭。澳门广场停车比较麻烦，车位不多，在停车场门口等了一会儿才进去。&#x0A;电梯上6楼，到前台验证信息后，服务员带我们入座。看到桌上的特价菜菜单，打算再点几个菜，但是服务员说享受了免费套餐就不可以点特价菜了，给了我们一张原价菜的菜单，比特价菜菜单贵了好多。&#x0A;套餐里的红烧猪手，炖的比较糯，微辣。东坡肉，第一次看到东坡肉这样的做法，切成片，跟青椒，笋干一起炒。豉油虾，虾是冰冻虾，软啪啪的。最抢手的是云南甜豆，清爽美味。最骗人的是辽参锅仔，辽参的影子都没看到，只有贡丸。&#x0A;另点了杂鱼煲和虾饺，虾饺一笼30元6个，像是蒸好后放了好久才端过来的，不热，温的，虾饺皮都破了。杂鱼煲89元，等了好久，催了几次才上，里面有鲳鱼，小黄鱼和豆腐鱼，裹了面粉油炸过再炖的，鱼只有上面一层，下面是满满的大蒜。&#x0A;服务员不大叫的动，茶水和湿巾是按位收的，结账时没有给停车券。', '[{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100g0v000000jiz43F5DA.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":23},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100a0v000000jjlsl18BD.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":23},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100j0v000000jhsqq08C3.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":25},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/10080v000000jih96C0BD.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":19},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/10020v000000jpd519E00.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":16},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/10070v000000jyyuu96A4.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":15},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/10060v000000jiwmd1F80.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":16},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/10030v000000jk0h7E003.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":13},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100i0v000000jh3pa553E.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":1},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/10060v000000jiwme0FA1.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":0}]', 0, '2018-08-02 10:37', NULL, 'michelle0519', 'https://images4.c-ctrip.com/target/fd/headphoto/g2/M06/32/5C/CghzgFW2Z_OAaQ-zAADQSLlA2fs772_C_180_180.jpg', 3.00, 1);
INSERT INTO `place_comment` VALUES (352, 'fd007c5e519a6a75a8f7296b', '名人名家&#x0A;现在这里出名的大概就是每一次不一样的特价菜吧。&#x0A;但是会有比较明显的两极化&#x0A;特价菜真的很便宜，但是除了特价菜以外，其它菜的性价比真的低得可怜。&#x0A;环境还是不错的，生意也非常好&#x0A;好像每家店的特价菜还不一样&#x0A;这里9.9的大虾和19.9的烧鸭必须点&#x0A;超级合算的感觉！吃下来几十块也能吃饱了&#x0A;比一般的快餐总要好上不少了～', '[{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/10060i0000009k1dqFBAE.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":18},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100b0i0000009k6h6284D.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":23},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/10040i0000009jrktA036.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":16},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100d0i0000009jqku1155.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":1},{\"pic_url\":\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/10060i0000009k1dt2C53.jpg\",\"pic_pv\":0}]', 0, '2017-07-26 23:25', NULL, '狮子啊', 'https://images4.c-ctrip.com/target/Z8090i0000009i1aoF543_C_180_180.jpg', 3.00, 1);
